  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个monitor总线的仲裁器，多个monitor source要共享一个统一的输出端口。我先画一下整体架构，你看看。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monitors",
        "monbus_arbiter",
        "Output"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，monitor source这边是M0、M1、M2到MN-1这样排列吗？还是固定就四个？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "M0",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "MN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用M0、M1、M2和MN-1表示，说明是可扩展的N个monitor。把它们包在Monitor Sources这个subgraph里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monitors",
        "M0",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "MN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，monitor sources画好了。那仲裁器内部怎么划分？需要几个功能模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "monbus_arbiter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "仲裁器内部我分四层：首先是Request Collection收集所有valid信号，然后是Arbitration Core做真正的仲裁算法，接着Backpressure处理反压，最后Select选出 winning packet。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Collect",
        "Arb_Core",
        "Backpressure",
        "Select"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Arbitration Core的算法具体支持哪些？我需要标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Arb_Core",
        "ARB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "支持三种：Round-robin、Weighted RR和Priority。配置寄存器可切换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB",
        "round",
        "weighted",
        "priority"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "仲裁核心标注好了。Request Collection这个模块具体做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Collect",
        "REQ"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "就是Gather所有monbus_valid信号，形成请求向量给仲裁器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Collect",
        "REQ",
        "monbus_valid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收集模块画好了。Backpressure那边是处理下游ready信号吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backpressure",
        "BP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Handle downstream backpressure，当下游没ready时要hold住当前选中的请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backpressure",
        "BP",
        "monbus_ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "反压模块完成。Select这边是做mux？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Select",
        "SEL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Mux winning packet to output，根据仲裁结果选通对应monitor的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Select",
        "SEL",
        "output"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "四个内部模块都画好了。输出端口怎么定义？",
      "elements_involved": [
